# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../clips.rst:289
msgid ""
"Slicing is a key feature for making precise edits and rearranging sections "
"of your video. You can slice a clip and choose to keep one side or both, and "
"with the ripple option, you can automatically shift other clips on the same "
